<div><a href="/2013/11/05/world/americas/canada-toronto-mayor-crack/index.html?iid=article_sidebar">Mayor Ford admits crack cocaine use, won't step down</a></div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx2">
updated 7:51 AM EST, Wed November 6, 2013
</div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx3">
<a href="/2013/11/05/world/americas/canada-toronto-mayor-crack/index.html?iid=article_sidebar"><img src="http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnn/dam/assets/131115123020-04-rob-ford-video-tease.jpg" alt="" border="0" height="68" width="120"/></a>
</div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx4">Despite the call for him to step aside after he publicly admitted using crack cocaine, Mayor Ford said he will not step down and will run for re-election next year.</div>
<div class="cnn_clear"></div>
</div></div></div>
<div class="cnn_stryspcvbx"><div class="cnn_stryspcvbxcntr"><div class="cnn_stryscbx1">
